## Actions & Navigation

### Button

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| variant | `"primary"`, `"secondary"`, `"link"`, `"danger"`, `"reaction"` | `"primary"` | Max 1 primary per section |
| size | `"sm"`, `"md"`, `"lg"` | — | Button size |
| text | `string` | — | Button label |
| icon | `string` | — | Font Awesome icon name |
| disabled | `boolean` | `false` | Disabled state |
| loading | `boolean` | `false` | Show loading spinner |
| fullWidth | `boolean` | `false` | Stretch to container width |
| link | `string` | — | Navigate to URL on click |

### Link
Text link for navigation.

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| href | `string` | — | Destination URL |
| color | `"default"`, `"body"`, `"muted"`, `"destructive"` | `"default"` | Link color style |
| icon | `string` | — | Leading icon |
| underline | `boolean` | `false` | Show underline |
| disabled | `boolean` | `false` | Disabled state |

### Nav
Navigation list — vertical sidebar or horizontal tabs.

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| orientation | `"vertical"`, `"horizontal"` | — | Direction; horizontal = tabs |
| variant | `"normal"`, `"subtle"` | `"normal"` | Visual emphasis |
| borderless | `boolean` | — | Remove borders |
| title | `string` | — | Section heading |

### BreadCrumbs
Page hierarchy trail. Children must be `BreadCrumbItem` components. Separator (`/`) is automatic.

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| text | `string` | — | Simple text crumb |

### Pill
Status/category indicator chip. Text is uppercase by default.

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| text | `string` | — | Label text (required) |
| variant | `"primary"`, `"neutral"`, `"success"`, `"warning"`, `"error"`, `"info"` | `"neutral"` | Color variant |
| textTransform | `"none"`, `"lowercase"` | — | Set `"none"` when Figma text is not uppercase |

**Gotcha:** `text` is **required** — use `text="Review"` (React) or `text: "Review"` (ERB). Never use JSX children `<Pill>Review</Pill>` — they are ignored.

### Badge
Small status tag for labeling items.

| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| text | `string` | — | Badge label |
| variant | `"neutral"`, `"primary"`, `"success"`, `"warning"`, `"error"`, `"info"`, `"notification"` | `"neutral"` | Color variant |
| rounded | `boolean` | `false` | Rounded pill shape |

**Gotcha:** Same as Pill — `text` is **required**. Use `text="+1000"` (React) or `text: "+1000"` (ERB), never JSX children.

