| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| icon | `string` | — | FA icon name (e.g., `"chevron-right"`) |
| size | `"xs"`, `"sm"`, `"lg"`, `"1x"`–`"10x"` | — | Icon size |
