| Prop | Values | Default | Notes |
|------|--------|---------|-------|
| size | `"sm"`, `"md"`, `"lg"` | `"md"` | Row density |
| container | `boolean` | `true` | Built-in Card wrapper |
| responsive | `"collapse"`, `"scroll"`, `"none"` | `"collapse"` | Mobile behavior |
| singleLine | `boolean` | `false` | Truncate cell text |
| disableHover | `boolean` | `false` | Remove row hover |
| striped | `boolean` | `false` | Alternating row colors |

### LabelValue
